        "input": "5 100 2 1000",
        "output": "1500",
        "explanation": "Explanation:\nChef bought 555 trees for 100100100 rupees, and then sold 222 trees for 100010001000 rupees, thus his profit was 2000−500=15002000 - 500 = 15002000−500=1500 rupees."
